    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nおはようございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nGood morning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.2666754961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、さくら\n遊園地からさくら宛に手紙が届いてるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Sakura.\nYou have a letter from the amusement park‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.8357611902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "私にですか？　そう言えば、この間のパレードライブが\n話題になってるって聞きましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To me? Speaking of which‚ I heard that the parade live\nbecame a hot topic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.3309183035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "あれのおかげで遊園地の知名度が上がって\n来場者数が一気に増えたそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to that‚ the amusement park's popularity has increased\nand the number of visitors has increased dramatically.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.4947876612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですね\n遊園地を盛り上げるお手伝いが出来て、私も嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so?\nI'm happy that I was able to help liven up the amusement park.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.3842833116,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9949.057833899986,
          "startTime": 234.3333411455
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "このお手紙、差出人がスタッフ一同になってますね\nええと、内容は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This letter‚ the sender is \"All Staff\".\nLet me see‚ the content is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.3333411455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr022.m4a",
      "text": "……私のライブがきっかけで、来月から\n遊園地のパレードを再開することになったそうです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…They said that they're going to resume the amusement park parade\nstarting next month‚ thanks to my live performance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.7000078122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr023.m4a",
      "text": "パレードの復活はスタッフの悲願だったから\nぜひお礼がしたいって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said they really want to thank you because reviving the parade\nwas their long-cherished wish…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.7666744788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr024.m4a",
      "text": "手紙と一緒に、遊園地の年間パスポートが入ってました\nこれがあればアトラクションも乗り放題だそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A yearly pass to the amusement park was included with the letter.\nThey said you can ride the attractions as many times as you like with this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.2666744788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr025.m4a",
      "text": "これを持って、今度はサニピのみんなと一緒に\n遊園地に行きたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to go to the amusement park\nwith this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.2000078122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr026.m4a",
      "text": "その時は{user}さんも\n一緒に遊びましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And {user}-san‚\nlet's have fun together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.9333248694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで遊びに行くのもいいが\n実はこの遊園地から新しいオファーが来ているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Going out to have fun together sounds great‚\nbut I actually have a new offer from this amusement park.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.9985507277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "またパレードライブをやりたいから、スケジュール\nさえ合えば、今度はサニピの五人で来てほしいそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said they want to do another parade live‚ and if your schedules align‚\nthey'd like all five Sunny Peace members to come this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.9170733064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr027.m4a",
      "text": "いいですね！\nみんなで遊園地をパレードするなんて絶対楽しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds great!\nParading through the amusement park with everyone will definitely be fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.6479805893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr028.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　いっそのこと、全国の遊園地で\nパレードをやりませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know! Why don't we do a parade at amusement parks\nall over the country?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 296.7666195471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr029.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースの日本縦断遊園地ツアーです！\n私達が全国の寂れた遊園地を盛り上げますよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It'll be Sunny Peace's Japan Amusement Park Tour!\nWe'll liven up all the deserted amusement parks in Japan~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 304.0132926851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "こらこら、寂れたとか言うんじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey. Don't say they're deserted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.8783539544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr030.m4a",
      "text": "わ、ごめんなさい！　でも……日本中の遊園地で\nライブするなんて想像しただけでワクワクしちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry! But… just imagining performing live\nat amusement parks all over Japan gets me excited!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 317.2978480774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_03-skr031.m4a",
      "text": "また一つ、楽しい思い出が出来そうです\nやっぱり私、遊園地が大好きです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like another fun memory is about to be made.\nI really love amusement parks!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 325.9999528805,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}